::DevilDuer/Zardus::

DevilDuer didn't need to be told twice. He jumps to the side, rolling 
out of Rage's way and firing his stun gun at her again, but this time 
the beam was slightly weaker.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus growls, rising into the air as he activates his jetpack. "I'm 
at the entrance," he replies to Feline, "There is a big bot here, and 
a group of bots on the way."

Zardus takes careful aim, firing a shot at Rage's head.
